  <script>
    // Array of titles
    var titles = [
        "Raw-Material",
          "COCOPEAT",
      "Sri Venkateshwara Coirs"
    ];

    // Function to change the title
    function changeTitle() {
      var titleElement = document.getElementById("title");
      var currentIndex = parseInt(titleElement.dataset.currentIndex);
      var nextIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % titles.length;
      titleElement.innerHTML = titles[nextIndex];
      titleElement.dataset.currentIndex = nextIndex;

      // Call the function again after 2 seconds
      setTimeout(changeTitle, 2000);
    }

    // Start changing the title
    setTimeout(changeTitle, 2000);
 </script>

// Helpers
function formatINRfromString(str) {
  // Accepts "â‚¹12,345.67" or 12345.67 and returns properly formatted INR string
  var n = typeof str === 'number' ? str : parseFloat(String(str).replace(/[^\d.-]/g, ''));
  if (isNaN(n)) n = 0;
  return n.toLocaleString('en-IN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'INR', minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 });
}

function updateTotals(resp) {
  if (resp.rawMaterialTotal) {
    $('#raw_amount_value').text(formatINRfromString(resp.rawMaterialTotal));
  }
  if (resp.ownerCashflowTotal) {
    $('#owner_amount_value').text(formatINRfromString(resp.ownerCashflowTotal));
  }
  if (resp.grandTotal) {
    $('#grand_amount_value').text(formatINRfromString(resp.grandTotal));
  }
}

  });
